data.description: FIRST TIME HOME BUYERS - This property qualifies to be purchased with 1% of the purchase price out of pocket from the Buyer. Credit and income restrictions may apply. Please contact our preferred lender for details. LOOK NO FURTHER!!! Come see this lovely home in Magnolia at West Side. Granite countertops and matching appliances gives the kitchen a modern and sleek look. The spacious master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom with double vanity, and separate shower.  The other three bedrooms are well-sized and shared a second bathroom.  The home located in the highly desirable Magnolia Community at West Side, known for its family friendly atmosphere and convenient amenities, Residents of this community enjoy access to a community pool, playground, and fenced dog park.  The neighborhood is also close to schools, shopping centers, restaurants, and all major attractions making it a convenient location for daily living.  The exterior of the home is equally impressive with a well-maintained lawn, attractive landscaping, and large vinyl fenced backyard.  The backyard is perfect for outdoor entertainment, with covered patio providing shade and a semi-covered seating area with its own BBQ enclosure. Whether you're hosting a cookout or simply enjoying a quiet evening outdoors, this backyard offers plenty of space and privacy.  Inside the home the open concept kitchen/dining and living room area creates a welcoming spacious atmosphere. Overall, this lovely home with freshly painted interior, included solar panels and water filtration system makes this the perfect place to call home.
